msgid ""
"<phrase condition=\"capitals-text\">Ada</phrase><phrase condition=\"capitals-"
"img\">da</phrase> loved Wednesdays. Every Wednesday, her mother and Alan "
"would pick her up from school, and they would all go to the library "
