#. (itstool) path: simplesect/para
#: Ada_Zangemann.dbk:788
msgid ""
"But that wasn’t all. With the software, they could give their skateboards "
"new, cool features. Marie attached colorful LED lights to her board that "
"glowed different colors depending on the speed. Konrad built old propellers "
